quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  30,25,"Hino jeyaa e maandeji Makko tindin…ói kattal e gootaaku Makko: tawde kammu ngun e leydi ndin no darorii yamiroore Makko ko aldaa e yanugol. Refti si o noddii noddaandu wutttugol Mala'ikaajo on allaandu ndu ka leydi, e jaka onon hi…óon yaltira e genaale mon …óen hasbeede yo…ìee."
  30,26,"Ko kanko tun woodani, laamagol e tagugol e toppital …ìen won…ìe ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Kala kon ko tagaa, ko …óoftii…ìe Mo jebbilanii yamiroore Makko."
  30,27,"Ko Kanko woni fu…ó…óor…óo tagugol ngol no ko aldah, e yeru gadii…óo refti O ruttita ngu …ìaawo gaynugol fii maggu. Awa fu…ó…óitagol ngol hino …ìuri fu…ó…óagol ngol welde fii, fow mun, …óin …ói…ói kala hino newanii Alla; tawde si O faandanike huunde, O daalanay nde tun: "Laato", nde laatoo. Hino woodani Mo Kanko teddu…óo maw…óo On, sifa …ìur…óo toowude on e kala ko O sifortee e sifaaji mawngu e timmal. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo Mo fooletaak, √ëee√±u…óo e tagu Mun e toppitagol Mun."
  30,28,"O piyanii on misal, onon …ìee sirkoo…ìe, ∆¥ettaangal e mon: Hara no woodani on e maccu…ìe mon …ìen e …ìen jeytir…óon √±aame mon renndaa…óo e jawle mon …óen, …ìe huloton senndodugol …óen jewle e mon, wano hulirton senndodugol e dimo hawtidu…óo e mon jawle? Hara on ja…ìanay …óum maccu…óo mon? Pellet on ja…ìataa …óum. Awa ko Alla …ìuri hanndude nde O ja…ìataa kafideede e tagu Makko (jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen) ka laamu Makko. Ko wano ngal misal piyirani mon, ngam Men …ìanngina hujjaaji e …ìanngannduyeeji sertu…ói, wonnde yim…ìe haqqil…ìe, tawde ko kam…ìe nafitorta …óum."
  30,29,"Wanaa waasde dalil woni sabu majjere ma…ì…ìe, wanaa waaseede …ìannginannede kadi. Majjere ma…ì…ìe nden, ko sabu jokkugol mbelee…óe e √±emmbugol baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe. Ko hommbo non fewnata mo Alla majjini? Hay gooto! Alanaa …ìe walloo…ìe ko du√±ana …ìe lepte Alla …óen."
  30,30,"Fewtiniri yeeso maa ngon, an Nulaa…óo e wondu- …ìe e maa …ìen, e diina Alla kan; acca kala diina si wanaa diina Makko kan. ∆äum ko diina lislaamu mo Alla tagiri yim…ìe …ìen e mun. Wa…ótitugol alaa e tagu Alla ngun. Ko …óum woni diina focciika kan; kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e yim…ìe anndaa wonnde ko …óum woni diina goonga."
  30,31,"Ruttoree e Makko tuubugol e junuubi mon, huliron Mo …óoftagol yamirooje Makko wo…ó…óitoo ha…óaa…ói Makko, √±inniron julde nden no timmiri, wata on jeye e sirkoo…ìe lunndii…ìe tagoodi ndin; …ìe kafida Alla e wo…ó…ìe goo ka dewe ma…ì…ìe,"
  30,32,"Wata on wa'u wa …ìen sirkoo…ìe waylunoo…ìe diina mun, …ìe goom…óini yoga …ìe yeddi yoga, …ìe wonti pecce-pecce, fedde kala e ma…ì…ìe no weltora meere wonnde ka ma…ì…ìe nden, kala yi'a ko ka√±um tun woni e goonga, …ìeya kan ko e meere woni."